We recommended that the Municipal Mayor instruct the:
• MGSO and the Supply Officer to stop the practice of drawing cash advances for payments to suppliers relative to the ICT Equipment acquisition; 
• Municipal Treasurer to ensure that payments are made thru issuance of checks directly to suppliers; 
• Municipal Accountant to submit all the lacking documents of the transactions; and 
• Bids and Awards Committee (BAC) and MGSO to strictly adhere with the audit procedures in performing the alternative modes of procurement.

In view of the foregoing, we recommended that the Municipal Mayor instruct the:
