Instruct the concerned officer to adhere to the procedures enumerated in Annex B of the Circular to be followed in the Receipt, Inspection, Acceptance and Recording of Deliveries of Semi-Expendable Property; Procedures in the Requisition and Issue of Semi-Expendable Property; and Procedures on the Transfer, Return, Re-issue and Disposal of Semi-Expendable Property.

We recommended to the management to –

Award procurement contracts to those suppliers with Lowest Calculated and Responsive bid only, otherwise; 

Include in the Instruction to Bidders or General Conditions in the RFQ that the LGU accepts partial bid so that it may award contracts to suppliers with partial bids but with lowest unit price.

