Require the heads of the departments/offices of the LGU to use the PPMP format prescribed by the GPPB (Annex D) and properly fill-up the required information especially as to the source of fund;

Require the BAC Secretariat to prepare the APP which reconciles with the budget proposal; and 

Forbid the BAC to commence any procurement activity without prior approved APP from the HoPE.

